- `development` @ 3f0364d — active (multi-provider + web UI)

## What was built (v0.4.0)
- [X] ProviderStore + ProviderHub (multi-provider OpenAI-compatible)
- [X] Namespaced model ids (provider/model-id)
- [X] Admin CRUD /admin/providers
- [X] Web dashboard at /dashboard (providers, models, routing)
- [X] Per-intent user preferences (pin models per intent)
- [X] Intelligent ladder fallback when no preferences set
- [X] Context window discovery + advertise
- [X] Exponential backoff on 429/5xx
- [X] 66 tests pass, ruff clean

## How it works
1. Add providers via web UI or API → their models appear on /v1/models
2. Configure per-intent routing (coding, chat, reasoning, etc.) via web UI
3. If no preferences → intelligent ladder picks best model across all providers
4. If preferences set → uses those models first, then falls back to ladder

